  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class EventPoolImportImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements EventPoolImport
    An implementation of the model object 'Event Pool Import'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Short Description
    • Name
    • Local Name
    • Include Local
    • Pool Size
